reviewText: Should be advertised better for smaller children
Stories and songs.  Songs are a bit annoying for an adult, but the six-year-old child loves them.  I recommend buying it.
Beautiful for the really little ones. Catchy songs you will find yourself singing to your little ones. A little hokey, but definitely a keeper!
Excellent video.  My daughter loves to sing along and dance with the video.  Very cute.
